{"tid":1812444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"〔主線任務 (期間限定)〕台灣手足需要大家，今個星期請關注台灣大選","createTime":"2020-01-05T13:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T17:43:31.000Z","uid":278057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37138498616b56aea739639215a0d537fbccb6e7","tid":1812444,"uid":278057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家諗下，如果韓國瑜上左位，成個局會點？</span></span><br />\n一．手足好可能被清算，到時要再逃亡或返香港被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二．美國少左台灣圍堵中國，中國壓力減少，就會對付我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>所以台灣在國際戰線上都好重要，侵侵幫左我地簽左民主人權法案，我地係時候幫返佢，等佢老人家專心對付中國。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下以下計算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQ2Bj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQ2Bj0.jpg&h=4bd73a4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小英文調係高，但年輕人投票率低，而支持韓國瑜的老人投票率高，此消彼長，韓係有機會贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要幫手叫年輕人投票先有機會嬴。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求求各位鍵盤戰士同暖氣軍師，叫身邊的台灣朋友一定要投3號小英，多佢一票就係多<br />\n黎緊一個星期，每日叫十個人就夠，同身邊的台灣朋友講又得，打online game時同台灣人講又得，係交友app宣傳又得。自己搵方法啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣組可以幫手出下圖，方便宣傳，另外如果星期六可以有活動關於台灣就最好</span><br />\n<br />\n我黎緊會係台灣交友app對台宣傳，大家有咩方法都可以提出，集思廣益。<br />\n以下係文字版，自行參考和修改。歡迎指正<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「親愛的台灣朋友，這是香港抗爭者對台灣人民的呼籲，不要信相韓國瑜的一國兩制，看看香港黑警以暴力毆打和平示威民眾，亂放催淚瓦斯等惡行，背後正是中國政府的極權打壓統治手段，可見台灣不會因中國而發大財，只會換來血的教訓。<br />\n<br />\n這半年的抗爭中，香港人已作出了重大的犧牲，有無數的市民被自殺，強暴，失去眼睛等。希望台灣不要重蹈我們覆轍，珍惜民主，珍惜手中的一票，懇請1月11日定必要回家投票，多你一票差很遠。<br />\n<br />\n投持小英，守護台灣，聲援香港」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"3d96acecbb5d23da957901335b6d8623dd7f2ccf","tid":1812444,"uid":278057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到"},{"pid":"ef2f50b7e0493394f004b5fade408d4b0d48b649","tid":1812444,"uid":278057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"9f777213ecafba883e2d8d5fbcb7dfe968064c35","tid":1812444,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"reddit 有台灣sub, 大家可以幫手推吓選舉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/taiwan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Ftaiwan%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=5e4d31ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/taiwan/</a>"},{"pid":"d81603f83b24b3745d725c508fbe59cd54c017d3","tid":1812444,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37138498616b56aea739639215a0d537fbccb6e7","tid":1812444,"uid":278057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家諗下，如果韓國瑜上左位，成個局會點？</span></span><br />\n一．手足好可能被清算，到時要再逃亡或返香港被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二．美國少左台灣圍堵中國，中國壓力減少，就會對付我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>所以台灣在國際戰線上都好重要，侵侵幫左我地簽左民主人權法案，我地係時候幫返佢，等佢老人家專心對付中國。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下以下計算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQ2Bj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQ2B